# Ignore everything in ~/.claude by default — this directory holds a lot of
# machine-local state (credentials, history, sessions, caches, projects, etc.).
*

# ...except the things worth version-controlling and sharing across machines:
!.gitignore
!README.md
!settings.json
!skills/
!skills/**
!package.json
!tests/
!tests/**

# ...but NOT the brot-plan scratch tracker — it lives at the repo root as
# BROT_PLAN.md and is gitignored per the brot skill convention (already covered
# by the `*` rule above; the durable record is the merged PRs, /brot-done deletes it).
/BROT_PLAN.md
